meta.name: TNA iMPACT!
meta.description: TNA iMPACT! is 2 hours of fast paced, innovative, usually high flying, sometimes brutal pro-wrestling. Featuring a mix of stars you know and love and new, up and coming talent, it'll blow away the cobwebs and leave you wanting more.

videos.overview: Ethan Carter the 3rd Goes for Kurt Angel's Heavyweight Championship Gold.

videos.title: The Reign of Carter
videos.overview: New TNA World Champion EC3 promises to defend his title 3 times in one night. Dixie Carter returns to Impact. Part 2 of the Jeff Jarrett interview. Velvet Sky vs Madison Rayne. Robbie E vs Jessie Goderz in a Streetfight.

videos.title: Carter vs. Carter
videos.overview: Who will Dixie Carter reveal as "The Law" in Impact Wrestling? Plus, all TNA Titles will be defended in this episode.

videos.title: Matt Hardy vs. Bobby Roode
videos.overview: Matt Hardy vs Bobby Roode; Bram vs Magnus; James Storm reveals his new partner; Eric Young vs Rockstar Spud.

videos.title: The 2015 TNA Hall of Fame
videos.overview: The 2015 TNA Hall of Fame; Magnus and Mickie James battle James Storm and Serena; Jeff Hardy returns. Brooke vs Marti for the TNA Knockouts Title.

videos.title: No Surrender EC3 battles Matt Hardy for the TNA Title in Full Metal Mayhem
videos.overview: No Surrender EC3 battles Matt Hardy for the TNA Title in Full Metal Mayhem. Bram vs Mr. Anderson. Gail Kim vs The Dollhouse. Austin Aries vs Rockstar Spud.

videos.title: Worlds Collide: TNA v. GFW
videos.overview: Jeff Jarrett is in control for the night; the main event is a King of the Mountain title match; Awesome Kong vs. Lei D Tapa; EC3 celebrates his TNA World Title victory; ``The Destroyer'' Lashley vs. Jessie Godderz.

videos.title: Turning Point
videos.overview: EC3 defends his title against PJ Black; Mr. Anderson battles Bram in an ``Open Mic Challenge''; Gail Kim faces Marti and Jade of The Dollhouse in `6 Sides of Steel'; Drew Galloway vs. Eli Drake in a No DQ match.

videos.title: Ring Leader Roulette
videos.overview: Jeff Hardy returns to IMPACT WRESTLING! Mr. Anderson vs James Storm vs Lashley vs Bobby Roode in a #1 Contender's Match for the KOTM Title. Will Dixie Carter appoint Jeff Jarrett to be the man in charge of IMPACT?

videos.title: Ethan Carter III defends the TNA World Title against Matt Hardy
videos.overview: Ethan Carter III defends the TNA World Title against Matt Hardy, with Jeff Hardy in his corner. Jeff Jarrett begins his hostile corporate takeover. PJ Black defends the King of the Mountain Title against Bobby Roode. Velvet Sky calls out The Dollhouse.

videos.title: Lethal Lockdown: Winner Takes TNA
videos.overview: "LETHAL LOCKDOWN" Team TNA battles Team GFW in "Lethal Lockdown" for complete control of TNA. Particpants include Lashley, Jeff Jarrett, Drew Galloway, and Eric Young. The Knockouts Title is on the line.

videos.title: EC3 vs. Rockstar Spud for the TNA World Title
videos.overview: EC3, with Jeff Hardy as his personal assistant, defends the TNA World Title against Rockstar Spud. The main event of "Bound For Glory" is determined in a 5 Way Elimination Match. Gail Kim vs Jade for the Knockouts Title.

videos.title: Countdown to Glory
videos.overview: TNA World Champion Ethan Carter III and Tyrus battle Drew Galloway and Matt Hardy in the main event. Dixie Carter shakes up the main event of Bound For Glory with a major announcement.

videos.title: World Title Series, Week 2
videos.overview: The World Title Series continues with the final four groups revealed. Matt Hardy starts his journey back to World Heavyweight Title.

videos.title: World Title Series, Week 3
videos.overview: Week 3 of the World Title Series sees Group Champions in action. EC3, Lashley, Anderson, Austin Aries in action.

videos.title: World Title Series, Week 4
videos.overview: Week 4 of the World Title Series features Matt Hardy, Abyss, and Drew Galloway in action. Plus Awesome Kong vs. Gail Kim.

videos.title: World Title Series, Week 5
videos.overview: The World Title Series heats up with action with pivotal matches featuring Eric Young, Eddie Edwards, Davey Richards & Bobby Roode.

videos.title: World Title Series, Week 7
videos.overview: The World Title Series continues with TNA Originals facing elimination matches. Bobby Roode faces "The Monster" Abyss while Eric Young goes on on one against James Storm. Awesome Kong faces Brooke from Group Knockout.

videos.title: World Title Series, Week 8
videos.overview: The final night of Group Play in the World Title Series. Every match the winner advances, while the loser goes home. The main event features "The Destroyer" Lashley against Austin Aries.

videos.title: World Title Series, Round of 8
videos.overview: Round eight of the TNA World Title Series determines who will advance to the semi finals; Matt Hardy vs. Jessie Godderz; Lashley vs. Shera; EC3 vs. Davey Richards; Eric Young vs. Tigre Uno.

videos.title: Final Face Off
videos.overview: Lashley, EC3, Matt Hardy and Eric Young face off one last time before the semi finals; Group Future 4 meets Group X Division; a four man battle occurs between Rockstar Spud, Mr Anderson, Bobby Roode and Eddie Edwards.

videos.title: Best of 2015, Part 1
videos.overview: The biggest matches and the most unforgettable moments of 2015, featuring Kurt Angle, Jeff Hardy, "The Destroyer" Lashley, Eric Young, Bobby Roode, and EC3.

videos.title: Best of 2015, Part 2
videos.overview: The biggest matches and the most unforgettable moments of 2015, culminating in the World Title Series.

videos.title: 1st Episode on POP TV LIVE!
videos.overview: TNA superstars battle it out in the six-sided ring for championship gold.

videos.title: The Beautiful People vs. The Dollhouse
videos.overview: New World Heavyweight Champion EC3 makes his first appearance since winning the title; Kurt Angle faces off against Drew Galloway; The Beautiful People face off against The Dollhouse.

videos.title: EC3 defends the World Heavyweight Championship
videos.overview: The World Heavyweight Championship is on the line; Gail Kim defends the Knockout Championship; The Wolves are in tag-team action; with Lashley, Jeff Hardy and others.

videos.title: TNA World Champion Matt Hardy makes his first appearance since his win
videos.overview: TNA World Champion Matt Hardy makes his first appearance since his win; ``Feast or Fired'' match; Awesome Kong battles Velvet Sky; Jeff Hardy, Beer Money, Lashley, and others also appear.

videos.title: TNA World Champion Matt Hardy faces off against Kurt Angle
videos.overview: TNA World Champion Matt Hardy faces off against Kurt Angle in the main event; The Wolves team up with Beer Money to face off against Eric Young, Bram, Abyss, and Crazzy Steve; EC3 speaks out; featuring Lashley, Drew Galloway, and others.

videos.title: EC3 returns for the first time since losing the TNA world title to Matt Hardy
videos.overview: EC3 returns for the first time since losing the TNA world title to Matt Hardy; the Kurt Angle Farewell Tour continues as he battles Drew Galloway; Awesome Kong faces Madison Rayne in Knockouts action. Also: Beer Money; Lashley; The Miracle Mike Bennett.

videos.title: EC3 and Matt Hardy continue their bitter feud over the world title
videos.overview: EC3 and Matt Hardy continue their bitter feud over the world title; The Wolves defend the tag-team titles against Decay in a "Monster's Ball"; Eric Young defends the King of the Mountain. Also featuring Kurt Angle; Gail Kim; and Beer Money.

videos.title: The Lockdown event in London
videos.overview: The Lockdown event in London features Matt Hardy vs. EC3; Beer Money vs. Eric Young and Bram; and the Dollhouse vs. Gail Kim and the Beautiful People.

videos.title: Kurt Angle battles longtime rival Bobby Roode
videos.overview: Kurt Angle battles longtime rival Bobby Roode; Drew Galloway goes one-on-one against "The Miracle" Mike Bennett with Maria.

videos.title: Kurt Angel's final match in TNA vs. Lashley
videos.overview: Kurt Angle faces off against ``The Destroyer'' Lashley in the main event; in a tag team match, The Wolves defend their titles against Beer Money; Gail Kim defends against Jade; King of the Mountain Title Match; with Matt Hardy, EC3 and others.

videos.title: Jeff Hardy, aka The Charismatic Enigma, returns seeking revenge
videos.overview: After Eric Young's vicious assault, Jeff Hardy, aka The Charismatic Enigma, returns seeking revenge; with Matt Hardy, EC3, Drew Galloway, The Miracle Bennett, and the Knockouts.

videos.title: Main Event: Jeff Hardy, Matt Hardy, EC3, and others battle in a Gauntlet Match
videos.overview: New TNA World Champion Drew Galloway learns the new number one contender as Jeff Hardy, Matt Hardy, EC3, and others battle in a Gauntlet Match; Beer Money defends the TNA Tag Titles in an open challenge; with The Miracle, Gail Kim and others.The scheduled matches are as follows:Beer Money vs Robbie E and Jessie GodderzEddie Edwards vs Crazzy SteveRebel vs Marti vs JadeMain Event: Jeff Hardy, Matt Hardy, EC3, and others battle in a Gauntlet Match

videos.title: Main Event: TNA World Heavyweight Champion Drew Galloway defends his title for the first time against Jeff Hardy
videos.overview: In the main event, World Champion Drew Galloway defends his title for the first time against Jeff Hardy; Velvet Sky faces Madison Rayne; with EC3, Matt Hardy and Beer Money.

videos.title: Main Event: TNA World Heavyweight Champion Drew Galloway vs. Matt Hardy for the TNA Heavyweight Championship
videos.overview: The following matches are scheduled on tonight's Impact Wrestling card:Street Fight match: The Pope vs. LashleySix Sides of Steel match: Jeff Hardy vs. Eric YoungMain Event: TNA Heavyweight Champion Drew Galloway defends his title vs. Matt Hardy

videos.title: Main Event: TNA World Heavyweight Champion Drew Galloway & Jeff Hardy vs. Matt Hardy & Tyrus
videos.overview: The scheduled matches for tonight's card are as follows:EC3 vs. "The Miracle" Mike BennettTNA World Tag Team Champions Beer Money defend their titles vs. TBAThe new TNA Knockouts Champion Jade makes her very 1st title defense vs. TBAMain Event: TNA World Heavyweight Champion Drew Galloway & Jeff Hardy vs. Matt Hardy & Tyrus

videos.title: Main Event: Matt Hardy vs. Jeff Hardy
videos.overview: The scheduled matches for tonight's card are as follows:Ladder match: Gail Kim vs. Maria vs. Jade vs. The Beautiful People vs. the DollhouseTNA X Division Champion Trevor Lee defends the X Division title against Eddie Edwards and DJZMain Event: Matt Hardy vs. Jeff Hardy

videos.title: Main Event: TNA World Heavyweight Champion Drew Galloway vs. Tyrus
videos.overview: The scheduled matches for tonight's card are as follows:EC3 vs. "The Miracle" Mike Bennett in a rematchTNA Wold Tag Team Champions Beer Money defend their titles vs. DecayMain Event: TNA World Heavyweight Champion Drew Galloway vs. Tyrus

videos.title: Main Event: Jeff Hardy vs Mike Bennett vs Bobby Lashley
videos.overview: Mike Bennett vs Jeff HardyJames Storm vs AbyssJade vs SiennaKing Of The Mountain match: Bram vs Eli Drake vs Eddie Edwards vs Jessie Godderz vs Michael EverettMain Event: Jeff Hardy vs Mike Bennett vs Bobby Lashley with Drew Galloway as the guest referee

videos.title: Main Event: EC3 vs. Rockstar Spud
Main Event: TNA World Champion Drew Galloway defends his title vs. "The Destroyer'' Lashley
videos.overview: In the main event, the TNA World Title is on the line as Drew Galloway defends his championship against "The Destroyer" Lashley, EC3 vs. Tyrus in a Last Man Standing Match and Jeff Hardy confronts Willow.

videos.title: Maine Event: Tyrus and Rockstar Spud vs Jeff Hardy
Main Event: Decay vs Drew Galloway
Main Event: Matt Hardy vs. Drew Galloway
videos.overview: EC3 and Gail Kim vs. The Miracle and Maria in a mixed tag-team match; Trevor Lee versus Eddie Edwards; with Drew Galloway, "The Destroyer" Lashley, Matt Hardy, and others.

videos.title: Gold Rush LIVE
videos.overview: Tonight's episode of Impact Wrestling is Gold Rush LIVE with 4 TNA titles on the line in separate matches. Newly crowned TNA World Heavyweight Champion Lashley will defend his title. The king of the Mountain Championship, The X-Division Championship and the TNA World Tag Team Championships will all also be on the line tonight. Eddie Edwards is the new X-Division Champion having won the title at Slammiversary 2016 this past Sunday.

videos.title: Main Event: Jeff Hardy vs. Matt Hardy
Main Event: Bobby Lashley vs. Ethan Carter III vs. Drew Galloway
Main Event: The Final Deletion match, Jeff Hardy vs. Matt Hardy
Main Event: Bobby Lashley vs Eddie Edwards
Main Event: Mike Bennett vs. Drew Galloway
Main Event: EC3 vs. The Miracle in the finals of the "Bound For Glory" Playoffs
videos.overview: EC3 vs. The Miracle is the main event in the finals of the Bound For Glory Playoffs; Eli Drake defends his King of the Mountain title against James Storm; Matt Hardy reveals his plans for himself and Jeff Hardy going forward.

videos.title: Main Event: Triple titles on the line - TNA World & X-Division Champion Lashley vs. King of the Mountain Champion "Cowboy" James Storm
videos.overview: Lashley meets ``Cowboy'' James Storm in a match; Lashley puts his World and X-Division titles on the line, while Storm puts his King of the Mountain title on the line; the winner will walk away with all three championships.

videos.title: Main Event: BROKEN Matt Hardy & Brother Nero vs. The Tribunal vs. The Helms Dynasty vs. The BroMans in a Fatal Four Way Tag Team Ladder Match to Determine The Number 1 Contender To The TNA World Tag Team Championship
videos.overview: Tonight's scheduled matches are as follows:Eddie Edwards vs. MooseJade vs. Gail KimDJ Zema Ion vs. Rockstar Spud vs. Mandrews vs. Braxton SutterEli Drake vs. Mahabali SheraMain Event: BROKEN Matt Hardy & Brother Nero vs. The Tribunal vs. The Helms Dynasty vs. The BroMans in a Fatal Four Way Tag Team Ladder Match to Determine The Number 1 Contender To The TNA World Tag Team Championship

videos.title: Turning Point - Main Event: A Battle Royal to become the number one contender for the TNA World Title
videos.overview: Former World Champions and friends collide as EC3 battles Drew Galloway with special referee, Aron Rex; a Battle Royal to become the number one contender for the TNA World Title.

videos.title: Main Event: TNA World Champion Lashley defends the World Title vs. "The Miracle" Mike Bennett;
videos.overview: TNA World Champion Lashley defends the World Title against ``The Miracle'' Mike Bennett; a new X-Division Champion is crowned as the stars battle in an Ultimate X Gauntlet Match, with DJZ, Trevor Lee and others; EC3 goes one on one with Eli Drake.

videos.title: Delete or Decay
videos.overview: A showdown takes place between the Hardys and Decay at the Hardy compound in North Carolina; Lashley and EC3 have their contract signing for the main event of ``Bound for Glory;'' Billy Corgan announces a new TNA Championship.

videos.title: The IMPACT Grand Champion Tournament continues
videos.overview: The IMPACT Grand Champion Tournament continues; Aron Rex takes on Trevor Lee; Eddie Edwards faces off against Shera; the Knockouts Gauntlet Match determines the number one contender for the Knockouts title; Braxton Sutter battles Rockstar Spud.

videos.title: Main Event: EC3 & Moose vs. Bobby Lashley & "The Miracle" Mike Bennett
videos.overview: During a tag team event, EC3 teams up with Moose to face off against Bobby Lashley and ``The Miracle'' Mike Bennett; Drew Galloway faces off against Eddie Edwards and Aron Rex battles Eli Drake during the semifinals.

videos.title: Road to GLORY
videos.overview: Road to Glory features Lethal Lockdown during which Team EC3 battles Team Lashley inside the 6 Sides of Steel; the captain of the winning team will pick the match stipulation for their BFG World Title Match; Reby Hardy versus Rosemary from Decay.

videos.title: Fallout from Bound for Glory
videos.overview: Fallout from the Bound for Glory match, with Lashley, EC3, the Hardys, Decay, Aron Rex, Drew Galloway, The Miracle, Maria, Gail Kim, and more.

videos.title: Main Event: Gail Kim vs. Maria for the Knockouts Title in a No Disqualification Match
videos.overview: Reactions to Eddie Edwards victory over Bobby Lashley for the World Title; in his in-ring debut, Cody goes one-on-one against The Miracle; Gail Kim faces Maria for the Knockouts Title in a No Disqualification Match.

videos.title: Double Main Event: Bobby Lashley vs. Moose & TNA World Champion Eddie Edwards vs. Cody
videos.overview: It's a double main event as Bobby Lashley goes one on one for the first time ever against Moose to determine the number one contender; World Champion Eddie Edwards defends his title for the first time against Cody.

videos.title: Main Event: Mike Bennett & Maria Kanellis vs. Cody & Brandi Rhodes in a Mixed Tag Team match
videos.overview: Allie vs. Laurel Van Ness, TNA Grand Champion Aron Rex and Eli Drake vs. Jessie Godderz and EC3Main Event: Mike Bennett & Maria Kanellis vs. Cody & Brandi Rhodes in a Mixed Tag Team match

videos.title: Main Event rematch: TNA World Champion Eddie Edwards vs. Bobby Lashley
videos.overview: In a rematch, TNA World Champion Eddie Edwards faces off against Bobby Lashley; plus, the Hardys go to battle against DCC; Aron Rex defends his Impact Grand Championship against Jessie Godderz.

videos.title: Main Event: TNA World Champion Eddie Edwards defends his title against Eli Drake
videos.overview: Eli Drake faces Eddie Edwards in the main event for the World Championship; qualifying matches start to determine the new number one contender, featuring The Miracle versus Moose, EC3 versus Abyss and more.

videos.title: Main Event: 4-Way dance to determine the New #1 Contender to the world title
videos.overview: It's a four-way battle to crown the new number one contender as EC3, The Miracle, Lashley, and Trevor Lee face off; Jeff Hardy returns looking for revenge; in tag action Brandi Rhodes must find a partner as she faces Laurel Van Ness and Sienna.

videos.title: Main Event: X Team Gold Elimination Match, DJZ, Braxton Sutter & Mandrews vs. Trevor Lee, Andrew Everett & Marshee Rocket
videos.overview: EC3 participates in a match against Eli Drake; if EC3 wins, Eli will not be allowed to speak for the rest of 2016; in an X Team Gold Elimination Match, DJZ, Braxton Sutter and Mandrews face Trevor Lee, Andrew Everett and Marshee Rocket.

videos.title: Main Event: Rosemary vs. Jade inside 6 Sides of Steel to crown a new Knockouts Champion
videos.overview: The Knockouts take center stage as Rosemary battles Jade inside 6 Sides of Steel to crown the new Knockouts Champion; Aron Rex issues an open challenge to the entire Impact roster to face him for the Impact Grand Championship.

videos.title: Main Event: TNA World Champion Eddie Edwards defends his title vs. EC3
videos.overview: World Champion Eddie Edwards defends his championship against number one contender EC3; Allie must fight for a spot on the roster as she goes one on one against Laurel Van Ness with Maria in her corner.

videos.title: Total Non-Stop Deletion
videos.overview: From Cameron, N.C., "Apocalypto'' is unveiled when Matt and Jeff Hardy defend their World Tag Team Titles in a revolutionary match.

videos.title: The Greatest Hits of 2016
videos.overview: The year's most memorable moments in Impact Wrestling, from Lashley's dominance to Kurt Angle's farewell to Gail Kim; featuring EC3, Drew Galloway, The Miracle, and many more.

videos.title: ...And a Hardy New Year
videos.overview: Broken Matt and brother Jeff Hardy revisit all of the top moments from 2016 for the Hardys, featuring highlights of The Final Deletion, Delete or Decay and Total Nonstop Deletion.

videos.title: Main Event: Eddie Edwards vs. Bobby Lashley vs. Ethan Carter III For The TNA World Heavyweight Championship
videos.overview: World Champion Eddie Edwards defends his title; after conquering Apocalypto, The Hardys announce what will come next for the greatest tag team in the world; Moose puts his Impact Grand Championship on the line.

videos.title: Main Event: The Hardy's defend the Tag titles vs. the Wolves
videos.overview: The Hardys defend their tag team titles against The Wolves; in a ``Last Man Standing Match,'' Lashley battles EC3.

videos.title: Main Event: It's the "Race for the Case'' as superstars battle for the right to future title shots
videos.overview: Drew Galloway makes his in-ring return to Impact Wrestling as he battles Moose for the Impact Grand Championship; it's the "Race for the Case'' as superstars battle for the right to future title shots featuring The Hardys, The Miracle and others.

videos.title: Genesis
videos.overview: Impact Wrestling presents "Genesis;'' the main event is a 30-minute Ironman Match for the World Title between Champion Eddie Edwards and his arch rival Lashley; plus, Rosemary defends the Knockouts Title against Jade in a Monster's Ball Match.

videos.title: Open Fight Night
videos.overview: "Open Fight Night'' returns as each of the four men who obtained a briefcase in the "Race for the Case'' will cash in their opportunity to challenge any opponent, in any match, with any stipulation they choose; with Jeff Hardy, DCC and others.

videos.title: What went down on Open Fight Night
videos.overview: What went down on Open Fight Night, including who challenged who, what predicament did the case holders put their opponents in and who came out victorious; with Drew Galloway, Broken Matt and Brother Nero

videos.title: Main Event: Brandi Rhodes & Moose vs. Crazzy Steve & Rosemary in a mixed tag match
videos.overview: Former World Champion Eddie Edwards addresses the situation from last week with his longtime tag partner and friend Davey Richards; Brandi Rhodes and Moose face off against Crazzy Steve and Rosemary in a mixed tag match.

videos.title: The wedding ceremony of Laurel Van Ness and Braxton Sutter
videos.overview: The wedding ceremony of Laurel Van Ness and Braxton Sutter; the X-Division title is on the line as Trevor Lee takes on former champion DJ-Z; Jessie Godderz faces another member of the DCC; the Hardys and their ``Expedition of Gold.''

videos.title: Main Event: Rosemary vs. Jade in a Last Knockout Standing match
videos.overview: Blushing bride Laurel Van Ness reacts to what happened during the ceremony; Rosemary and Jade face off in a Last Knockout Standing match; giants collide in the main event when Bobby Lashley puts his title on the line against Josh Barnett.

videos.title: Main Event: Bobby Lashley vs. Alberto El Patron for the TNA World Heavyweight Championship
videos.overview: World Champion Lashley shares what's next; the feud between former Tag Team Champions Eddie Edwards and Davey Richards escalates; stars of the high-flying X Division go into action.

videos.title: Brandi Rhodes makes her IMPACT singles debut
videos.overview: Alberto El Patron, who faced Lashley last week, shares his thoughts concerning the World Championship; Brandi Rhodes makes her IMPACT singles debut; the X-Division title is on the line.

videos.title: Main Event: Davey Richards with Angelina Love vs. Suicide
videos.overview: Davey Richards, accompanied by Angelina Love, takes on Suicide; Reno Scum sees action again; LAX takes on the DCC; a special guest arrives in the six-sided ring.

videos.title: The high flyers of the X Division see action as Andrew Everett takes on DJZ
videos.overview: The high flyers of the X Division see action as Andrew Everett takes on DJZ; the tag team division takes center stage when Decay, Reno Scum, Laredo Kid, and Garza and LAX battle it out; tempers flare between the Knockouts.

videos.title: Main Event: Davey Richards vs. Eddie Edwards in a Last Man Standing match
videos.overview: Two men once viewed as brothers put their bodies on the line as Davey Richards and Eddie Edwards face off in a Last Man Standing match; Josh Mathews and Jeremy Borash decide who will represent them in a tag team event.

videos.title: Main Event: Team Josh vs. Team Jeremy in an eight-man tag team match
videos.overview: In team tag action, Allie steps into the ring alongside her man, Braxton Sutter, to get her hands on Sienna, who teams with her cousin, KM; Team Josh takes on Team Jeremy in an eight-man tag team match.

videos.title: Main Event: TNA Heavyweight Champion Lashley defends his title vs. James Storm
videos.overview: With the Knockouts Championship on the line, Rosemary defends against Knockout original ODB; the World Tag Team Champions, LAX, see action; James Storm and Bobby Lashley go one on one for the World Championship.

videos.title: Main Event: Tag Team Champions LAX defend their titles vs. Decay
videos.overview: Newly crowned X-Division champion Low Ki appears; the Veterans of War team debuts; Moose defends his IMPACT Grand Championship against Chris Adonis; Tag Team titles are on the line when defending champions LAX go to war with former champions, Decay.

videos.title: Main Event: GFW World Champion Magnus defends his title vs. Alberto El Patron

videos.title: Episode 39
videos.overview: History will be written when The Hardys and Team 3D meet face-to-face for the official signing of their Bound For Glory showdown. Frankie Kazarian and Jake Something team up against Steve Maclin and the returning Mr. Anderson. Knockouts action with Jody Threat facing Victoria Crawford. A Call Your Shot Qualifier Battle Royal with the winner getting the number 20 spot in the Call Your Shot Gauntlet at Bound For Glory. X-Division Champion Leon Slater and Cedric Alexander take on The Rascalz in tag team action. Plus, we hear from Knockouts World Champion Ash By Elegance.

videos.title: Episode 40
videos.overview: In the main event, the TNA Knockouts World Tag Team Titles are on the line as The Elegance Brand defends against The IInspiration. New TNA International Champion Frankie Kazarian hosts "The King's Speech" with new TNA Knockouts World Champion Kelani Jordan. Tasha Steelz of Order 4 collides with Alisha Edwards of The System. Nic Nemeth goes one-on-one with The Home Town Man. Plus, the Angel Warriors are in action.

videos.title: Episode 43
videos.overview: TNA Studios presents Bound For Glory: Fade to Black. Follow the stars of TNA Wrestling as they prepare for the biggest event of the year. See the emotion, the passion, and an up-close look behind the scenes. Plus, witness an encore presentation of the TNA World Championship match between Trick Williams and Mike Santana.

videos.title: Episode 44
videos.overview: On a special edition of TNA iMPACT!, celebrate A Very Hardy Halloween. Enter a universe unlike any other as Matt and Jeff Hardy open the gates to their world, The Hardy Compound. Go inside the minds of The Hardys as they relive some of their favorite Broken memories.

videos.title: Episode 45
videos.overview: The road to Turning Point continues as Open Fight Night makes its highly anticipated return for the first time since 2017. Anyone can make a challenge, and everyone must accept! When the opportunities are endless, what chaos will unfold?

videos.title: Episode 48
videos.overview: Celebrate Thanksgiving with the stars of TNA Wrestling. On this special edition of iMPACT!, the Thanksgiving Turkey Bowl returns as Ryan Nemeth, Brian Myers, Mance Warner, Trey Miguel, Eric Young and The Home Town Man face off. Plus, Trick Williams and Mustafa Ali vs. Leon Slater and Mike Santana.
